<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:15:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登呼吁加大处罚力度、加强管制以应对美国芬太尼危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-calls-bigger-penalties-more-controls-fight-us-fentanyl-crisis-2024-07-31/</link><description>据一位高级政府官员称，总统乔·拜登计划周三呼吁对毒品走私者实施更严厉的处罚，并对药丸压榨商和​​进口商进行更严格的控制，作为应对美国阿片类药物危机的新措施的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 09:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-calls-bigger-penalties-more-controls-fight-us-fentanyl-crisis-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国铁木摊贩抗议处罚政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-temu-vendors-protest-over-penalty-policy-2024-07-31/</link><description>一名参与抗议的商家告诉路透社，Temu 上的数百名中国卖家抗议该公司施加的难以忍受的高额罚款，这是与低成本竞争对手 Shein 进行激烈价格竞争的新迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:42:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-temu-vendors-protest-over-penalty-policy-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>欧莱雅首席执行官预计中国下半年将出现“小幅负增长”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-ceo-expects-slightly-negative-h2-growth-china-2024-07-31/</link><description>欧莱雅首席执行官 Nicolas Hieronimus 周三表示，中国美容市场下半年将保持“小幅下滑”，此前这家法国公司报告第二季度增长慢于预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:21:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-ceo-expects-slightly-negative-h2-growth-china-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部称美国不是南海问题当事方</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-is-not-party-south-china-sea-issue-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周三表示，美国不是南海问题的当事方，并警告菲律宾，拉拢其他国家挑起对抗将破坏地区稳定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 07:49:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-is-not-party-south-china-sea-issue-says-chinese-foreign-ministry-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在解放军成立周年纪念日前呼吁加强边防</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-calls-strong-border-defences-ahead-pla-anniversary-2024-07-31/</link><description>据官方新华社周三报道，中国国家主席习近平呼吁建设强大的边海空防御体系，保护国家领土主权和海洋利益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-calls-strong-border-defences-ahead-pla-anniversary-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯开始第三阶段战术核演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-starts-third-stage-tactical-nuclear-drills-2024-07-31/</link><description>俄罗斯国防部周三表示，俄罗斯已开始第三阶段演习，练习部署战术核武器。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:18:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-starts-third-stage-tactical-nuclear-drills-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国经济增长放缓，西门子医疗未能实现第三季度预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-misses-q3-expectations-due-slow-china-2024-07-31/</link><description>德国医疗技术公司西门子医疗 (Siemens Healthineers) 周三报告称，由于中国订单持续延迟，第三季度销售额和盈利低于预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:31:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-misses-q3-expectations-due-slow-china-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国对外国芯片设备向中国出口新规定豁免部分盟友</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-us-rule-foreign-chip-equipment-exports-china-exempt-some-allies-sources-say-2024-07-31/</link><description>两位熟悉该规则的消息人士称，拜登政府计划下个月公布一项新规则，该规则将扩大美国阻止某些国家向中国芯片制造商出口半导体制造设备的权力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:29:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-us-rule-foreign-chip-equipment-exports-china-exempt-some-allies-sources-say-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行股价因 30 亿美元回购而上涨；称增长对降压影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-reports-flat-first-half-profit-beats-estimates-2024-07-31/</link><description>汇丰控股周三宣布进行 30 亿美元的回购，并上调了收入前景，因为该公司在其战略方面取得了进展，以确保其业务免受全球降息可能影响贷款回报的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 04:19:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-reports-flat-first-half-profit-beats-estimates-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行任命乔纳森·宾厄姆为临时首席财务官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-names-jonathan-bingham-interim-cfo-2024-07-31/</link><description>汇丰控股周三任命 Jonathan Bingham 为其临时集团首席财务官，自 9 月 2 日起生效。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 04:15:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-names-jonathan-bingham-interim-cfo-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国共产党开除中石油前董事长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-former-cnpc-chairman-party-secretary-2024-07-31/</link><description>官方媒体周三称，中国执政党共产党以违纪为由，对国有企业中国石油天然气集团公司（CNPC）原董事长、党委书记王宜林给予开除党籍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-former-cnpc-chairman-party-secretary-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国疲软的工厂PMI暴露了出口巨头的痛点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-july-factory-activity-shrinks-services-grow-more-slowly-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三的一项官方调查显示，由于工厂努力应对新订单下降和价格低廉的问题，中国的制造业活动在 7 月份跌至五个月最低点，这表明这个世界生产大国的下半年将陷入困境。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-july-factory-activity-shrinks-services-grow-more-slowly-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行加息后股市上涨，日元上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-31/</link><description>日本央行以出人意料的鹰派立场加息，引发日元上涨，周三欧洲股市追随亚洲股指走高。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:21:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势导致油价反弹，但中国数据限制涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-claws-back-some-losses-after-israel-retaliates-against-hezbollah-2024-07-31/</link><description>伊朗哈马斯领导人被杀加剧中东紧张局势后，周三石油期货从七周低点反弹逾一美元，但由于对中国需求疲软的担忧，价格仍面临压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 00:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-claws-back-some-losses-after-israel-retaliates-against-hezbollah-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：今年市场最重要的一天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-30/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 21:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>